<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Donation Events — Vihaan's Vision</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css" />
</head>
<body>

<header class="topbar">
  <a class="brand" href="/" aria-label="Vihaan's Vision home">
    <span class="logo-mark">☀️</span>
    <span class="logo-copy">
      <strong>Vihaan's Vision</strong>
      <small>A world where every child smiles</small>
    </span>
  </a>
  <nav>
    <a href="/">Home</a><a href="/events/">Events</a><a href="/donate/">Donate</a><a href="/donation-events/" style="color:#2f6f9f">Donation Events</a><a href="/team/">Team</a><a href="/contact/">Contact Us</a>
  </nav>
</header>


<main>
  <section class="page-hero">
    <span class="kicker">Donation Events</span>
    <h1 class="page-title">Past gifts. Future smiles.</h1>
    <p class="lead">
      This page can show all donation events already completed and the events planned for the future.
      Add photos, dates, partner names, number of gifts, and stories as the project grows.
    </p>
    <div class="actions">
      <a class="btn primary" href="#past">Past Events</a>
      <a class="btn gold" href="#future">Upcoming Events</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="past">
    <h2 class="section-title">Donation Events I Have Done</h2>
    <p class="section-intro">
      Donation events and photos will be added here as the project grows.
    </p>

    <div class="timeline">
      <article class="timeline-item">
        <div class="timeline-date">Completed</div>
        <div>
          <span class="badge">Past Event</span>
          <h3>UCSF Children’s Hospital Keychain Donation</h3>
          <p>
            I created and donated 3D Printed keychains for UCSF Children’s Hospital as part of my effort
            to bring joy to children through small, thoughtful gifts.
          </p>
          <p>
            <strong>Impact to add:</strong> number of keychains donated, date, and photos from the donation.
          </p>

          <div class="photo-grid" aria-label="UCSF Children’s Hospital donation photos">
            <div class="photo-placeholder">
              <div>
                <span>📸</span>
                Donation photo
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <p class="class-note">
            Donation photos from this event will be added here.
          </p>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="timeline-item">
        <div class="timeline-date">Completed</div>
        <div>
          <span class="badge">Past Event</span>
          <h3>Community Support Collection</h3>
          <p>
            I collected donations and class contributions to help buy filament and supplies for future gift batches.
          </p>
          <p><strong>Impact to add:</strong> amount raised, supplies purchased, next batch goal.</p>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="future" class="band">
    <h2 class="section-title">Upcoming Donation Events</h2>
    <div class="story-box">
      <p>Upcoming donation events will be announced soon.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>

<footer>
  <p>☀️ A world where every child smiles — one gift, one child, one ray at a time.</p>
</footer>
</body>
</html>
